This is a problem solver for 3-dimensional geometrical qualitative problems for high schools.

Installation

    1. install CLIPS to your system:

        http://clipsrules.sourceforge.net/

    1. install XClips to your system:

        https://github.com/agentzh/xclips

    2. Build this project via Gnu make:

        make

    3. Run the test suite

        make test

Check the (Chinese) documentation for how to use this program:

    * http://agentzh.org/misc/vrg/Overview.html

    * http://agentzh.org/misc/vrg/KB.html

